org.afplib.afplib

Interface MDD

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SF
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MDDImpl

    public interface MDD
extends SF
    A representation of the model object 'MDD'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Xm Base
    • Ym Base
    • Xm Units
    • Ym Units
    • Xm Size
    • Ym Size
    • MDD Flgs
    • Triplets

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getMDD()
